title: Calculus for Scientists and Engineers
description:
this is an excellent text.  you can (and should) buy it for >$100.  im a poor student and i paid full price for it (twice).  i try to be good most of the time.  however the hard copy that i purchased began to fall apart and rather than refund my purchase, they told me to "shove it".  so i present to you a recently cracked azw4 from which a pristine pdf has been extracted.  other torrents posted here and on kat offer large pdfs scanned from this 2013 edition.  this is not a scan, it is the real thing.  download, share, enjoy and refuse to tolerate publishers who take advantage of you.

i will be seeding daily between the hours of 3am and 8am EST
